http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Visakhapatnam/Dial-1912-for-power-supply-problems/article14636389.ece

The Chairman and Managing Director of Andhra Pradesh Eastern Power Distribution Company Limited (APEPDCL) M.M. Nayak, has appealed to consumers of the Discom to dial 1912 to register complaints.The number is toll free and available to all consumers from the five districts of Srikakulam, Vizianagaram, Visakhapatnam, East Godavari and West Godavari.General electricity supply problems such as low-voltage and damaged transformers, replacement of the damaged electricity network instruments, will be addressed with a complaint lodged through the 1912 number, he added.People need not come to the Discom’s office or visit the local centres, to lodge complaints.